      "comment": "MIKE'S HOPE (5) resumes. He showed good ability in two runs last campaign, in the market on debut at Cranbourne when third before a solid effort in town. That form has worked out fairly well and with natural improvement this time around he'll go close. IMMORTALISED (3) has been good in two runs back at Pakenham Synthetic and should be at peak fitness now. He'll take holding out. SIBUN (7) stuck on well fresh at Ballarat Synthetic when beaten a length and will come on from that. He should take catching. Doubt anything else is a serious chance but WRITTEN BY BETSY (10) is perhaps next best if she can improve sharply.",
